Hadramaut, Hadhramaut, Hadramout, Hadramawt ama Ḥaḍḍūt (Carabi: حضرموت ناش: a Mus: 𐩢𐩳𐩧𐩣𐩩) waa gobol ku yaal koonfurta dhammaadkii jasiiradda Carabta. Magaca ayaa si rasmi ah loo sii hayay Guddoomiye ku xigeenka Hadhramaut ee Jamhuuriyadda Yaman. Dadka Hadhramaut waxaa loogu yeeraa Hadhrami iyo Hadhrami Carabi.
